N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 147.5 - Procedure in a sex offense part

State Regulations

Each case transferred from a local
criminal court to the Supreme Court or County Court and referred for
disposition to a sex offense part thereof shall be subject to the same
substantive and procedural law as would have applied to it had it not been
transferred. Notes
